      "body" : "Hm. I've tested and it doesn't rescan on start after importing a key.\r\n\r\nFun example from IRC related to this:\r\n00:18 < master5o1> ugh bitcoin-qt keeps crashing when i try to importprivkey\r\n00:18 < master5o1> =/\r\n00:18 <@gmaxwell> master5o1: What do you mean by crashing?\r\n00:18 < master5o1> okay\r\n00:18 < master5o1> i mean freezing\r\n00:18 <@gmaxwell> ...\r\n00:19 <@gmaxwell> It's not crashing.\r\n00:19 <@gmaxwell> It can take on the order of 10 minutes to rescan when you import a key. \r\n00:19 <@gmaxwell> (depending on how fast your disk is, on a fast ssd its much less)\r\n00:19 < master5o1> oh.\r\n",
